title: AWS EBS: Burst Balance
agents: aws
catalog: cloud/aws
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors burst balance of AWS EBS.
 To make this check work you have to configure the related
 special agent {Amazon Web Services (AWS)}.

 You can configure upper levels for {WARN}/{CRIT} (no default levels are set).

 The service goes {WARN}/{CRIT} if the burst balance exceed these levels.

item:
 Name of the instance

inventory:
 One service is created for each volume if all required metrics (Burst Balance) are given.
